name: PhantomIXRowStyle
description:
PhantomIXRowStyle - Preserving a Legacy Model

Seen it requested in several communities, the creator nuked it and all information associated with it but this model produces amazing results.

This is not my work and I don't plan to support this, just trying to preserve this amazing model for the community.

I don't have a safetensors version and won't be creating one.

Update: added safetensors version

(will keep the ckpt just for legacy reasons, they are both pruned)

Looking forward to seeing what people create with it.

Prompting / Info

  • Doing NSFW and SFW are equally possible and doesn't require much effort.

  • This model likes to do really detailed muscle line art so it helps to negative it out if you don't want it.

  • CLIP SKIP 1 or 2 seems to produce equally interesting results.

  • I don't show it - but this model works wonders in combination with LORAs and Hypernetworks.

  • This model is one of the best (IMO) for producing simplified color palettes without needing to go into crazy color tone prompting,

    • I love combining it with other styles to get a nice simplified palette and simple line work.

    • It has really creative lighting passes that are not overly complex.

Acknowledgments / Credits

  • I think the model author was https://huggingface.co/Cosk but the Cached Page got 404'd

  • Credit to the original artist PhantomIXRow

    • I never knew about them until I found this model and think their art is really fantastic.
